y available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard warning\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Niestandardowy:</strong> This feature is non-standard and is not on a standards track. Do not use it on production sites facing the Web: it will not work for every user. There may also be large incompatibilities between implementations and the behavior may change in the future.</p></div><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"podsumowanie","title":"Podsumowanie","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Powoduje wyświetlenie łańcucha znaków w określonym rozmiarze czcionki, tak jak to było w znaczniku&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/font\"><code>&lt;font&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sk.c5.82adnia","title":"Składnia","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><code><var>str</var>.fontsize(<var>size</var>)</code></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parametry","title":"Parametry","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"size\"><code>size</code>&nbsp;</dt>\n <dd>Liczba całkowita pomiędzy 1 a 7, łańcuch znaków reprezentujący rozmiar znaku liczby całkowitej między 1 a 7.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"opis","title":"Opis","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Kiedy określisz rozmiar jako liczbę całkowitą, ustaw rozmiar <code>stringName</code> na jeden z 7 innych rozmiarów. Kiedy określisz <code>size</code> łańcucha znaków jako \"-2\", to dostosujesz rozmiar czcionki <code>stringName</code> relatywnie do rozmiaru jaki został ustawiony w znaczniku <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Fonts\"><code>&lt;basefont&gt;</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przyk.c5.82ady","title":"Przykłady","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przyk.c5.82ad_zastosowanie_metody_string_do_zmiany_rozmiaru_.c5.82a.c5.84cucha_znak.c3.b3w","title":"Przykład: Zastosowanie <strong><code>fontsize()</code></strong>","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js  language-js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> worldString <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Witaj, Świecie\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>worldString<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">small</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>     <span class=\"token comment\">// &lt;small&gt;Witaj, Świecie&lt;/small&gt;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>worldString<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">big</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>       <span class=\"token comment\">// &lt;big&gt;Witaj, Świecie&lt;/big&gt;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>worldString<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">fontsize</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">7</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// &lt;fontsize=7&gt;Witaj, Świecie&lt;/fontsize&gt;</span></code></pre></div>","titleAsText":"Przykład: Zastosowanie fontsize()"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"zobacz_tak.c5.bce","title":"Zobacz także","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String/big\"><code>String.prototype.big()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String/small\"><code>String.prototype.small()</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Podsumowanie","id":"podsumowanie"},{"text":"Składnia","id":"sk.c5.82adnia"},{"text":"Opis","id":"opis"},{"text":"Przykłady","id":"przyk.c5.82ady"},{"text":"Zobacz także","id":"zobacz_tak.c5.bce"}],"summary":"Powoduje wyświetlenie łańcucha znaków w określonym rozmiarze czcionki, tak jak to było w znaczniku <font> (en-US).","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"String.prototype.fontsize()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"String.prototype.fontsize()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"String.prototype.fontsize()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"String.prototype.fontsize()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"String.prototype.fontsize()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"String.prototype.fontsize()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"String.prototype.fontsize()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/string/fontsize","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/string/fontsize/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web","title":"Technologie Internetowe dla developerów"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript","title":"JavaScript"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference","title":"Dokumentacja referencyjna JavaScript"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects","title":"Obiekty"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String","title":"String"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String/fontsize","title":"String.prototype.fontsize()"}],"pageTitle":"String.prototype.fontsize() - JavaScript | MDN","noIndexing":false}}